Daga: ritley@uimrl7.mrl.uiuc.edu () Subject: neman THERMOCOUPLE amfilifa kewaye
Ina so a iya fadada wani irin ƙarfin lantarki sigina wanda yake shi ne fitarwa daga wani thermocouple, zai fi dacewa da a factor of 100 ko 1000 ---- sabõda haka, sakamakon irin ƙarfin lantarki za a iya ciyar da mafi sauƙi a cikin wani sirri-kwamfuta na tushen Dogarin data saye katin.
Domin kowa ya sami damar nuna mini zuwa nassoshi ga irin haihuwarka?
Na ga mai sauki amfilifa haihuwarka a gabãnin haka, kuma amma nĩ ba ka tabbatar da yadda da su yi aiki a aikace.
A wannan yanayin, Ina son wani abu da zai fadada isasshe &quot;da kyau&quot; da za a yi amfani da thermocouples (sunã cẽwa, &#39;yan digiri daidaito ko mafi alhẽri).
Duk wani pointers za a ƙwarai nuna godiya!
